# Business Requirements Document (BRD)
## After Sales Performance Dashboard
### Version 1.0 – Prepared for: Automotive BI Platform

---

## 1. Introduction
The **After Sales Performance Dashboard** is a unified analytical tool designed to evaluate the operational and financial performance of workshop activities across multiple brands (Peugeot & Mitsubishi).  
The dashboard provides daily/monthly monitoring of labor, parts, oil, and tire revenues, profitability trends, achievement vs target, and workshop job-card behavior.

This dashboard forms a core component of the **Automotive BI Platform**, enabling management to make informed decisions and identify underperforming KPIs or branches.

---

## 2. Business Objectives
The dashboard aims to achieve the following objectives:

- Provide a single performance view for multi-brand aftersales operations  
- Track daily and monthly KPIs (Labor / Parts / Oil / Tires)  
- Identify performance gaps between **Actual vs Target**  
- Monitor workshop profitability  
- Track customer behavior through job card analysis  
- Enable brand-level and model-level performance comparisons  
- Support decision-making for operational and financial improvements  

---

## 3. Scope of the Dashboard

### In Scope
- Revenue analysis for:
  - Net Labor
  - Net Parts
  - Net Oil
  - Net Tires
- Daily & Monthly aggregations  
- Actual vs Target comparison  
- Workshop Profit  
- Model performance (based on Parts revenue)  
- Brand-level filtering  
- Branch-level performance  
- Job Cards filtering (Paid, Excluding Warranty & Internal)

### Out of Scope
- Direct Sales (POS revenue)  
- AR/Aging analysis  
- Expense performance  
- Financial liquidity KPIs  
- Warranty performance  

---

## 4. Data Sources

### 4.1 ERP Systems
- **Peugeot ERP** (Autoline instance)
- **Mitsubishi ERP** (Separate database with identical structure)

Both systems share the same schema but stored separately.  
Data is unified after cleansing and transformation.

### 4.2 Tables Used
| Table | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| JC_Header | Job Card main info |
| JC_Lines | Labor, Parts, Oil, Tires details |
| DirectSales_POS | Direct parts sales (independent) |
| Targets | Monthly KPI targets (Excel sheet) |
| Models | Brand → Model → YearModel mapping |
| Branches | Workshop branches |

### 4.3 Refresh Frequency
- Daily refresh @ 6:00 AM  
- Monthly target update

---

## 5. User Personas

| Role | Usage |
|------|--------|
| After Sales General Manager | Full performance review |
| Workshop Manager | Daily operations tracking |
| Parts Manager | Parts revenue & model performance |
| Finance Controller | Profitability validation |
| CEO/COO | Monthly executive performance |

